    def __init__(self, config: Dict[str, str]) -> None:
        super().__init__(config)
        self._code_prompt_text = AGENT_PROMPT
        self.dependencies = AutomagikAgentsDependencies(...)
        self.tool_registry.register_default_tools(self.context)
```

**Tool Registration**:
```python
